TAPTAP PRIVACY POLICY
Updated May 26, 2023
TapTap (“we”) highly values the privacy of our online visitors and users, and that is why we will protect your personal information by complying with applicable laws and implement industry accepted security standards. Our products and services are provided by TAPTAP PTE. LTD. with the registered address at 111 SOMERSET ROAD #05-11 SINGAPORE (238164).
This Privacy Policy ("Policy") sets out the basis which we may collect, use, disclose or otherwise process your personal data and help you understand the measures we take in acquiring, using, managing and protecting your personal information. However, this policy does not apply to the practices of companies that we do not own or control, or to the people we do not employ or manage.
Please read carefully and make sure you understand the contents of this Policy before using our services. By registering or using our services, you expressly acknowledge that you have read, understood and accepted the following terms. In the event you do not agree to any of the terms, you may immediately stop using our services.
Some key provisions regarding your personal information rights and interests are indicated in bold. Your use of such services shall constitute your acceptance of the provisions
.
